org.acra.jraf.android.util.activitylifecyclecallbackscompat
Class MainLifecycleDispatcher

java.lang.Object
  org.acra.jraf.android.util.activitylifecyclecallbackscompat.MainLifecycleDispatcher
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActivityLifecycleCallbacksCompat
public class MainLifecycleDispatcher
extends Object
implements ActivityLifecycleCallbacksCompat

Keeps a list of ActivityLifecycleCallbacksCompats that will be called following the life cycle of the application's activities. This class is used when the app is running on an older platform version that does not support Application.registerActivityLifecycleCallbacks(ActivityLifecycleCallbacks) and Application.unregisterActivityLifecycleCallbacks(ActivityLifecycleCallbacks).
